I stand before you today to plead guilty to the charge of being drunk and disorderly.

I take full responsibility for my actions and acknowledge that I was in the wrong. On the day in question, I made a poor decision to prioritize my own relaxation and disregard the impact it would have on others. I deeply regret my lack of control in that situation and the negative consequences that followed.

