I want to acknowledge a previous conviction of careless driving from 10 years ago. While this incident does not excuse my behavior on the day in question, I want to emphasize that it was an isolated incident and not indicative of the person I strive to be. I have learned from that mistake and have taken steps to ensure that such behavior is not repeated.

