While counseling may not be my preferred choice, I am open to alternative measures that the court deems appropriate to address the harm caused by my actions. I am willing to undertake rehabilitation or intervention programs suggested by the court to rectify my behavior and prevent any recurrence.

Thank you, Your Honour, for allowing me the opportunity to address the court and express my deep remorse for my actions.

